-- Rafael Nadal Wins Wimbledon First Round Match Against Japan's Nishikori
-- James Cone
-- 2010-06-22T15:42:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/rafael-nadal-wins-wimbledon-first-round-match-against-japan-s-nishikori.html

          
          
             Rafael Nadal, playing his first
match at Wimbledon since winning the title in 2008, beat Japanâ€™s
Kei Nishikori in straight sets in the opening round of the
tournament today.  
 The Spaniard, who missed the grass court Grand Slam last
year with a knee injury, won 6-2, 6-4, 6-4 on Centre Court at
the All England Club.  
 Nadal, winner of his seventh Grand Slam title earlier this
month at the French Open, is the top-ranked player on the ATP
Tour, but is seeded No. 2 at Wimbledon.  
          
          


  


        